headline: Cycle Pharmaceuticals Launches Its First Oncology Product, PHYRAGO™ (dasatinib) Tablets, in the US
summary: DETROIT, October 16, 2025--Cycle Pharmaceuticals announces the launch of PHYRAGO, its first oncology product in the US. PHYRAGO is launched in partnership with Handa Therapeutics, LLC, and will be exclusively available through specialty pharmacy Onco360® with a specialty distribution network from McKesson, Cencora, and Cardinal Health.
